{"tid":1964588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續罷食!抗疫資助食肆無封頂 美心「大包圍」可擸半億","createTime":"2020-04-09T02:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T05:23:59.000Z","uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef5782292349f2a5d476402358b45ec5e32e756e","tid":1964588,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》翻查食環署牌照網頁，其中美心集團旗下最少有151間持牌普通食肆，當中包括美心皇宮、翠園及潮江春等酒樓，也包括千両、元氣壽司等食肆。根據資助計劃，每間持牌並營運中的食肆均可向政府申請20萬元資助，若以此推算，美心集團旗下的持牌食肆，可從抗疫基金申領高達3,020萬元資助。<br />\n<br />\n此外，小食食肆、食物製造廠、烘製麵包餅食店等持牌人亦可獲8萬元資助。翻查食環署牌照網頁，美心西餅、東海堂及星巴克分別為持牌烘製麵包餅食店、食物製造廠及持牌小食食肆，合共約237間，若全數均符合資格並向政府申請資助，推算可從抗疫基金申領1,896萬元資助，即約388間「美心系」分店，合共可申領高達4,916萬元資助。美心集團回覆查詢時稱不評論。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200409/QMVLEJWHAR7AJJ7XSH24X4KUQU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200409%2FQMVLEJWHAR7AJJ7XSH24X4KUQU%2F&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbhY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=a94996dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200409%2FQMVLEJWHAR7AJJ7XSH24X4KUQU%2F&h=684b0df9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200409/QMVLEJWHAR7AJJ7XSH24X4KUQU/</a>"},{"pid":"f8d3b05938f615b22ec3c90e65250f2c435b9593","tid":1964588,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:39:58.000Z","msg":"記住罷食呀手足們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb7e15fec1929d650d35b4f4cb1f38cb64626c6","tid":1964588,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"幫藍店回血"},{"pid":"576c1e4eeaba9ec1a4634788b1c86e68e4e6bb0a","tid":1964588,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/09/ePfiy4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%